When you purchase a commission, you are paying someone to work to your specs, using their time and focus to produce work for you. Work that might not help them grow or pay bills.

Art isn't an exclusive luxury, but being able to afford skilled labourer is.

Art is available to anyone all the time. literally follow an artist and look at the media tab on their twitter, beautiful art.

However, their time and labour is not free.
